metadata.name: SuperLuckyBox.ETH
metadata.description:
This piece was created for my good friend and avid supporter Chris AKA SuperLuckyBox.ETH I am extremely thankful to have met Chris and honored to be able to create this work for him. The intent of this piece was to be used as a twitter banner and is based off of a physical canvas that was painted for him as well. Thank you for all of your support Chris and I hope this new banner serves your profile well <3  
Stay Optimistic & Always Rise
